Hmmm, I wonder which one put snoot marks all over the door right after I cleaned it 🙈😂

We got Herb looking like a frat boy that’s up to no good.

Buddy, who looks like he’s had one too many to drink.

Daisy looking like a brat sticking her tongue out.

Then Charlie looking like he’s just over today.
